HEADWORD: Seaworthy
<hw>Sea"wor`thy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Fit for a voyage;
worthy of being trusted to transport a cargo with safety; <as>as, a
<ex>seaworthy</ex> ship</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
